# Experimental Logs

This document summarizes experiments conducted to evaluate the robustness of the **GIT-Large image captioning model** against adversarial transfer attacks.
The defense method explored is **LoRA-based adversarial fine-tuning** using a mixture of clean and adversarially perturbed images.

Dataset: Flickr8k
Evaluation set size: 1000 images

---

# 1. Baseline Model (Pretrained GIT-Large)

### Model

* Architecture: microsoft/git-large
* Training: No additional fine-tuning
* Dataset: Flickr8k

### Attack Configuration

* FGSM attack (ε = 8/255)
* MI-FGSM attack (ε = 8/255, α = 2/255, 10 iterations)

