# 2. LoRA Adversarially Fine-Tuned Model

### Training Configuration

| Parameter              | Value               |
| ---------------------- | ------------------- |
| Base Model             | microsoft/git-large |
| Fine-tuning Method     | LoRA                |
| LoRA Rank              | 4                   |
| LoRA Alpha             | 8                   |
| Learning Rate          | 2e-5                |
| Batch Size             | 4                   |
| Epochs                 | 5                   |
| Maximum Caption Length | 50                  |

### Training Data Composition

The training dataset contains a mixture of clean and adversarially perturbed images.

* Clean images: 60%
* FGSM adversarial images: 20%
* MI-FGSM adversarial images: 20%

Total training samples: **25,000**

