# Observations

* The baseline model shows significant degradation in caption quality under adversarial perturbations.
* Adversarial fine-tuning improves robustness against both FGSM and MI-FGSM attacks.
* Although some reduction in semantic similarity (BERTScore) is observed after fine-tuning, the model exhibits improved stability under adversarial conditions.
* The mixed training distribution enables the model to maintain reasonable caption quality while increasing resistance to perturbations.

